headline: Philip Morris International Presents at 2025 Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference
summary: STAMFORD, CT, December 02, 2025--Regulatory News: Philip Morris International Inc. (PMI) (NYSE: PM) Chief Executive Officer, Jacek Olczak, will address investors today at the Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference.
